Meets my expectations and even more.

I've used a few other astrology apps, AstroMate takes the cake. Although the UI is a little ugly it contains all the information I look for: numerology, horoscopes, natal charts, etc. all in one place and in an easily readable format. No more text walls, just simple sections for the information I'm looking for. The purchase price is a little high but I haven't regretted it which is wonderful. Well done.
